---
<section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="badge">Professionnel & Rapide</span>
            <h1>Votre expert de confiance pour <span>tous vos projets</span></h1>
            <p>Une courte description pour mettre en avant votre proposition de valeur, votre expérience et pourquoi vos clients vous adorent.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
                    Obtenir un devis gratuit <i class="ph ph-arrow-right"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="#services" class="btn btn-secondary">
                    Nos services
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-features">
                <div class="feature"><i class="ph-fill ph-check-circle"></i> Intervention 48h</div>
                <div class="feature"><i class="ph-fill ph-check-circle"></i> Devis Gratuit</div>
                <div class="feature"><i class="ph-fill ph-check-circle"></i> Qualité Garantie</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
</section>

<style>
    .hero {
        position: relative;
        padding: 10rem 0 6rem;
        background-color: #0f172a;
        color: white;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-bg {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark));
        opacity: 0.2;
        clip-path: polygon(20% 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);
    }

    .hero-container {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
    }

    .hero-content {
        max-width: 650px;
    }

    .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 span {
        color: var(--primary);
    }

    p {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: #cbd5e1;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .hero-actions .btn {
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .hero-features {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .feature {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    .feature i {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; }
        .hero-bg { width: 100%; opacity: 0.1; clip-path: none; }
    }
</style>
